data.chText: （海运、空运或陆运的）货物；货运
data.enText: goods that are transported by ships, planes, trains or lorries/trucks; the system of transporting goods in this way
to send goods by air freight
to send or carry goods by air, sea or train

data.chText: 使充满（某种心情或口气）
data.enText: to fill sth with a particular mood or tone
Each word was freighted with anger.

means: 使充满(某种心情或口气)

ex.chText: 我们收到从古巴运来的两船货物。
ex.enText: We received two shipments from Cuba.

ex.chText: 这批货没有达到你们通常的标准。
ex.enText: This shipment is not up to your usual standards.

ex.chText: 我们来此是要对最近的一批货提出索赔。
ex.enText: We are here to claim the latest shipment.

synonyms.bx: 指由某处运往他处的一批货物。

ex.chText: 轮船载着大量货物驶往纽约。
ex.enText: The ship sailed for New York with a lot of cargo.

ex.chText: 船上一半的货物被倒进了海里。
ex.enText: Half of cargo on the ship was poured into the sea.
This plane can carry a cargo of 16 tons.

synonyms.bx: 指用轮船或飞机长距离运载的货物。

ex.chText: 这辆卡车装载了许多吨货物。
ex.enText: The truck carried many tons of freight.

ex.chText: 这些货物必须小心搬运。
ex.enText: This freight must be carefully handled.

synonyms.bx: 指海运、空运或陆运的货物。

ex.chText: 一些货物在运输中丢失了。
ex.enText: Some goods were lost in transit.
The goods were consigned by railway.

synonyms.bx: 指铁路或公路运载的货物。

tr: transporting goods commercially at rates cheaper than express rates
goods carried by a large vehicle
the charge for transporting something by common carrier
example: the freight rate is usually cheaper

value.def: Freight is the movement of goods by lorries, trains, ships, or aeroplanes.

example.ex: France derives 16% of revenue from air freight.
example.tran: 法国 16%的岁入来自航空货运。

value.def: Freight is goods that are transported by lorries, trains, ships, or aeroplanes.

example.ex: 90% of managers wanted to see more freight carried by rail.
example.tran: 90%的经理希望看到更多的货物经由铁路来运输。

value.def: When goods are freighted, they are transported in large quantities over a long distance.

example.ex: From these ports the grain is freighted down to Addis Ababa.
example.tran: 粮食从这些港口运到亚的斯亚贝巴。

trans: 货运转运商，货物运输报关行，货物传送装置
国际海运；海运业务；海运；海运费；海运运费
远洋运费，海运运费；缩写词为OF
运费由提货人支付；运费到付
